page.title: 15WYTON
page.content: Wyton is situated on the road from Bilton and Sproatley. It was found by John De Wyton. There is a big hall in the background but nobody lives in it. It is falling down and the windows are smashed. Most of the buildings in Wyton are bungalows and there are some big houses which people live in. There are three farms and one chapel. There are 45 houses and bungalows altogether. Wyton is such a small place that there are no shops at all in Wyton and the people who live there have to go into Bilton for their nearest shopping facilies.
